1. *Ona* je nosila *prsten* na sredini prsta. (She was wearing a ring on the middle finger.)
2. *Prsten* je bio izrađen od zlata. (The ring was made of gold.)
3. *Prsten* je bio velik i prelep. (The ring was big and beautiful.)
4. Ona je nosila *prsten* oko vrata. (She was wearing a ring around her neck.)
5. Ona je imala *prsten* sa svim dragim kamenjem. (She had a ring with all the precious stones.)
6. Ona je imala *prsten* koji je bio ukrašen dragim kamenjem. (She had a ring that was adorned with precious stones.)